								<div class="title" id="post-title-3839130">
																		100 Articles. 001 proposal. S &amp; C Plastics Tale.
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164139" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;" >Ihp</a></span> <span class="odate time_1529255684 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">17 Jun 2018 17:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3839130">
									

<p>A few random, disjointed thoughts:</p>
<p>The intended title for this is &quot;Story of Your Life&quot;. I would put it up on the 001 page, but apparently it's locked against editing. Yaaaay.</p>
<p>Mood Music: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u9vOwc-6t-8">Matchbox 20: Let's See How Far We've Come</a>. Alternatively: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F5OJPUXJvHk">Mob Choir: 99</a></p>
<p>I've had four or five ideas for an 001 proposal since I came onto this site. Among them were:</p>
<ul>
<li>A puzzle box that acted as a source of most of the anomalies</li>
<li>An 001 proposal explaining why travelling to alternate universes was a bad idea</li>
<li>The literal serpent from the Wanderer's Library</li>
</ul>
<p>This is the only one that's stuck. It's a combination of a tale from the S &amp; C Plastics canon (which you should seriously read), an 001 proposal about the world being fictional, and is probably one of the longest-winded things I've ever written.</p>
<p>I've written more than 100 articles for this wiki, obviously, but as of this article, I have 100 surviving pages on the wiki, according to <a href="http://www.scpper.com">SCPper</a> (which counts things such as hub pages and author pages, whereas Jarvis doesn't). I wanted to make my 100th article big&#8230; and then y'all went and wrote about four 001 proposals in the space of a week. I know, I'm sick of 'em too. Lemme have this.</p>
<p>A few people have joked about an S &amp; C Plastics 001 in the past. Well, you know what they say: don't let your memes be dreams. Also if I ever say that again, strangle me. The canon was originally started by Djoric, who I shamelessly stole it from and took over like it was a child I snatched from the crib. He doesn't seem to mind, though. But yeah, S &amp; C Plastics 001 proposal. Let's hope it survives.</p>
<p>Thanks to everyone who critted, including but not limited to: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529258226" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multizig" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3740504); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3740504&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529258226" alt="multizig" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3740504)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multizig" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3740504); return false;">multizig</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529258226" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;">DrChandra</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529258226" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a