														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3839204">
									

<p>I'm a little on the fence about the proposal referencing other 001's like Swann's and Clef's, I figured if you do it well enough, you can make it work.</p>
<p>But my problem with this is that it relies too heavily on Swann's proposal as leverage for me to count it as an original proposal in any sense of the word.</p>
<p>Donr get me wrong. The storytelling is superb, the meta is far better than Swann's, but I just can't look beyond the issues of it relying so heavily on Swann's for me to count as a 001 proposal.</p>

